H3.text: Jenny Shipley was the first female prime minister of which country. Nz

A4.text: Dame Jennifer Mary Shipley is a New Zealand former politician who served as the 36th prime minister of New Zealand from 1997 to 1999.

A5.text: She was the first female prime minister of New Zealand, and the first woman to lead the National Party.
